      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I highly doubt 20MHz at 3.3V is realistic without wait states. My own testing put the switching speed of the GPIOs at 12.5MHz at 3.3V.",
